import React from 'react'
import { Container,Row,Col  } from 'react-bootstrap'

function Footer() {
  return (
    
        <footer>
          
          <Container>

          <Row>
            <Col>
            Footer
            
            </Col>
          </Row>
          </Container>
          </footer>
    
  )
}

export default Footer
